00:30:06,048 --> 00:30:07,548
うわ…おお！
Whoa... Oh!

473
00:30:07,548 --> 00:30:09,048
嘘でしょ、魔法のノーム…？
Oh my god, is that a gnome with magic...?

474
00:30:09,048 --> 00:30:10,548
しかも死んだ！
And it's dead!

475
00:30:10,548 --> 00:30:12,048
ノームを殺しちゃった！
You killed a gnome!

476
00:30:12,048 --> 00:30:13,548
めっちゃ…魔法の妖精キノコ？
Very... magic fairy mushroom?

477
00:30:13,548 --> 00:30:14,548
魔法の妖精ノームだよ。
Magic fairy gnome.

478
00:30:14,548 --> 00:30:16,548
あれってピザ？ / そう、ピザ！ピザを撃て！
Is that a pizza? / Yeah, pizza! Shoot the pizza!

479
00:30:16,548 --> 00:30:18,048
ピザを撃て！ピザ！
Shoot the pizza! Pizza!

480
00:30:18,048 --> 00:30:19,548
ピザって悪者なの？
Pizza's a bad thing?

481
00:30:19,548 --> 00:30:21,048
待って、ピザを撃つべきなの？
Wait, we're supposed to shoot the pizza?

482
00:30:21,548 --> 00:30:23,548
おお、おお…ダメ、ダメ！
Oh, oh... No, no!

483
00:30:23,548 --> 00:30:25,548
待って、ダメ！あの子はただの幼い女の子だよ！
Wait, no! She was just a little girl!

484
00:30:25,548 --> 00:30:27,548
ダメ！ただの女の子だったのに！
No! She was just a little girl!

485
00:30:27,548 --> 00:30:29,048
死ね！
Die!

486
00:30:29,548 --> 00:30:31,548
違う、違う、違う、ロイヤルガードだよ！
No, no, no, that's a royal guard!

487
00:30:31,548 --> 00:30:33,548
リズ！セシリア！
Liz! Cecilia!

488
00:30:34,548 --> 00:30:36,548
ちょっと！うわ、彼女人殺しだよ！
Hey! Whoa, she's a killer!

489
00:30:36,548 --> 00:30:38,548
待って、見て！運転中にメールしてる！
Wait, look! He's texting while driving!

490
00:30:38,548 --> 00:30:40,048
死んだ！
He's dead!

491
00:30:40,048 --> 00:30:42,548
いいね、いいね！犯罪者を一人駆除できた！
Good, good! We got rid of a criminal!

492
00:30:42,548 --> 00:30:44,048
そう、あいつは紛れもない犯罪者だ。
Yeah, that's a criminal right there.

493
00:30:44,048 --> 00:30:45,548
ちょっと、それ私の年金！
Hey, that's my pension!

494
00:30:45,548 --> 00:30:47,548
ああ、そう、それ撃て！彼女の年金を撃ち抜け！
Oh, yeah, shoot that! Shoot her pension!

495
00:30:47,548 --> 00:30:49,048
そうだ！彼女の年金を撃て！
Yes! Shoot her pension!

496
00:30:49,048 --> 00:30:51,548
あら、こんにちは、ちっちゃなジェットパック。
Oh, hello, tiny jetpack.

497
00:30:51,548 --> 00:30:53,048
すっごく小さいね。
Very tiny.

498
00:30:53,048 --> 00:30:55,048
よし！ナイスショット！
Yes! Nice shot!

499
00:30:58,048 --> 00:31:00,048
ピクルス…見て、見て…きゅうり…
Pickle... look, look... cucumber...

500
00:31:00,048 --> 00:31:01,548
きゅうり、きゅうりだ…
Cucumber, cucumber...

501
00:31:01,548 --> 00:31:03,048
きゅうりは撃っちゃダメ！
Don't shoot the cucumber!

502
00:31:03,048 --> 00:31:04,548
きゅうり！
Cucumber!

503
00:31:04,548 --> 00:31:06,548
よし！ナイス！ / イェーイ！
Yes! Nice! / Yay!

504
00:31:07,048 --> 00:31:09,048
待って…そう、私たちは…
Wait... yeah, we...

505
00:31:09,048 --> 00:31:11,048
あ、クッキー食べてるノームを見て！
Oh, look at the gnome eating cookies!

506
00:31:11,048 --> 00:31:13,048
クッキーだ！よし、よし！バイバイ！
Cookies! Yes, yes! Bye-bye!

507
00:31:13,048 --> 00:31:14,048
本当に？
Really?

508
00:31:14,048 --> 00:31:15,048
できた！
I did it!

509
00:31:15,048 --> 00:31:18,048
全部撃ち抜いたね！ / イェーイ！
She shot everything! / Yay!

510
00:31:19,048 --> 00:31:21,048
セシリアの最終スコアは…
Cecilia's final score is...

511
00:31:24,048 --> 00:31:27,048
…7ポイント！ / え、7？ / 7。
...seven points! / Oh, seven? / Seven.

512
00:31:27,048 --> 00:31:30,048
6、7？なんで7？
6, 7? Why seven?

513
00:31:30,048 --> 00:31:32,048
8、9？ / まあ…
8, 9? / Well...

514
00:31:32,048 --> 00:31:34,048
正直なところ…
Honestly...

515
00:31:34,048 --> 00:31:38,048
きゅうりはマイナスだと思うんだけど、プラスだと思ってたの…
I think the cucumber was a minus, and I thought it was a plus...

516
00:31:38,048 --> 00:31:40,048
だってきゅうりを処分すれば、彼女が食べなくて済むから。
...because we want to kill the cucumber so she doesn't have to eat it.

517
00:31:40,048 --> 00:31:41,548
私はきゅうりが嫌いだからね、そうだ。
I don't like cucumbers, right.

518
00:31:41,548 --> 00:31:44,048
それに、時には撃っちゃいけないターゲットを撃っちゃったとしても…
And I think even if I shot the ones that weren't meant to be shot sometimes...

519
00:31:44,048 --> 00:31:45,548
このおバカさん…
You idiot...

520
00:31:45,548 --> 00:31:48,048
危機的状況では、たとえ間違っていても決断を下さなきゃいけないんだよ！
...in a crisis situation, you just have to make a decision, even if it's the wrong one!

521
00:31:48,048 --> 00:31:50,048
撃て！それはどうかな…
Shoot! Not sure about...

522
00:31:54,048 --> 00:31:56,048
よし、いくぞ。フレイムオン！
All right, let's go. Flame on!

523
00:31:56,048 --> 00:31:59,048
フレイムオン！いいぞ。
Flame on! All right.

524
00:31:59,048 --> 00:32:03,048
3、2、1、スタート！
3, 2, 1, go!

525
00:32:04,048 --> 00:32:05,548
イェーイ！
Yay!

526
00:32:05,548 --> 00:32:07,048
よし、撃て！撃て！
Okay, shoot it! Shoot it!

527
00:32:07,048 --> 00:32:09,048
撃て！いいね！
Shoot! Good!

528
00:32:09,048 --> 00:32:11,048
あら、チアリーダーだね。
Oh, she's a cheerleader.

529
00:32:11,048 --> 00:32:13,048
撃て！撃て！撃て！
Shoot it! Shoot it! Shoot it!

530
00:32:13,048 --> 00:32:14,548
ふう！仕留めたぞ！
Phew! Got that one!

531
00:32:14,548 --> 00:32:17,048
私の頭が…やらなきゃ…
My head... I must...

532
00:32:17,048 --> 00:32:18,548
なんで自分を撃っちゃうの？！
How could you shoot yourself?!

533
00:32:18,548 --> 00:32:20,048
待って、明らかに違う…
Wait, it's obviously not...

534
00:32:20,048 --> 00:32:22,048
ダメ、ダメ、ダメ！あれは鳥だよ！鳥！
No, no, no! That's a bird! That's a bird!

535
00:32:22,048 --> 00:32:24,048
可愛い鳥なのに！
That's a nice bird!

536
00:32:24,048 --> 00:32:26,048
ああ、そうね、ハハ。
Oh, yeah, haha.

537
00:32:26,048 --> 00:32:28,048
うわ、うわ、うわ…また？
Whoa, whoa, whoa... again?

538
00:32:28,048 --> 00:32:30,048
なんで自分を撃ったの？
Why did you shoot yourself?

539
00:32:30,048 --> 00:32:32,048
そんなつもりじゃなかったんだ。
I didn't mean to do that.

540
00:32:32,048 --> 00:32:33,548
わかった。
Okay.

541
00:32:34,048 --> 00:32:36,048
よし、見てみよう。
Okay, let's see.

542
00:32:36,048 --> 00:32:39,048
あら見て！撃たなかった！わあ、ハハ。
Oh, look at that! She didn't shoot! Wow, haha.

543
00:32:39,048 --> 00:32:41,048
地面に落ちてるのは1ペニー？
Is that a penny on the ground?

544
00:32:41,048 --> 00:32:44,048
待って、これ撃たないの？なんで？
Wait, she's not shooting this one? Why not?

545
00:32:44,048 --> 00:32:46,048
ダメ、私の年金！リズ、それが必要なの！
No, my pension! Liz, we need that!

546
00:32:46,048 --> 00:32:48,048
年金？ダメ、必要だよ！
Pension? No, we need it!

547
00:32:48,048 --> 00:32:51,048
そうだ！正義のためにそれが必要なんだ！
Yeah! We need that for justice!

548
00:32:52,048 --> 00:32:54,048
お願い！
Please!

549
00:32:54,048 --> 00:32:57,048
私のピザ！ああ、お腹空いた！お腹空いた！
My pizza! Oh, oh, I'm hungry! I'm hungry!

550
00:32:57,048 --> 00:32:59,048
よし、仕留めた！やった！
Yeah, she got it! Yes!

551
00:32:59,048 --> 00:33:01,048
ピザが食べたい！
We want pizza!

552
00:33:01,048 --> 00:33:03,048
オッケー。
Okay.

553
00:33:03,048 --> 00:33:05,048
お金！お金！お金！
Money! Money! Money!

554
00:33:05,048 --> 00:33:07,048
撃て、撃て！お金が必要なんだ！
Shoot it, shoot it! We need money!

555
00:33:07,048 --> 00:33:10,048
お金、お金、お金！お金が必要！なんで？！
Money, money, money! We need money! Why?!

556
00:33:10,048 --> 00:33:13,048
なんで？！嘘でしょ、リズ…
What?! Oh no, Liz...

557
00:33:13,048 --> 00:33:15,048
あ、猫ちゃんを見て！
Oh, look at the cat!

558
00:33:15,048 --> 00:33:17,048
殺せ！殺せ！殺せ！
Kill it! Kill it! Kill it!

559
00:33:17,048 --> 00:33:19,048
ダメ！殺して！
No! Kill it!

560
00:33:19,048 --> 00:33:22,048
でも、あいつすごく面白いよ！
He's so funny, though!

561
00:33:22,048 --> 00:33:24,048
よし、最後だ。「私を撃って」！
All right, last one. Shoot me!

562
00:33:24,048 --> 00:33:25,548
撃て、撃て！
Shoot it, shoot it!

563
00:33:25,548 --> 00:33:28,048
その調子！ふう、仕留めた！
Like that! Phew! Got them!

564
00:33:28,048 --> 00:33:32,048
イェーイ！すごい！よし、終わりだよ！
Yeah! So good! Okay, you are done!

565
00:33:32,048 --> 00:33:34,048
ああ、やった！よし、私のスコアは？
Oh, yes! Okay, what is my score?

566
00:33:34,048 --> 00:33:37,048
あなたの得点は…ドラムロール…
Your points are... drumroll...

567
00:35:00,056 --> 00:35:01,356
No, that's bad!

568
00:35:01,356 --> 00:35:03,356
Oh! Kill it! Kill it!

569
00:35:03,356 --> 00:35:06,856
I can't... I can't hit it.

570
00:35:07,556 --> 00:35:09,556
Oh, God.

571
00:35:10,056 --> 00:35:12,556
You're lucky. You're lucky. You're so lucky right now.

572
00:35:13,256 --> 00:35:17,556
Kill it! Kill it! / No, don't kill it!

573
00:35:18,056 --> 00:35:20,556
I can't kill it. I looked into its eyes and I can't kill it!

574
00:35:21,056 --> 00:35:24,056
I looked right into its eyes and I couldn't do it!

575
00:35:24,056 --> 00:35:25,556
Pizza!

576
00:35:25,556 --> 00:35:28,556
Yeah! Good job!

577
00:35:29,056 --> 00:35:32,556
No more pizza. / No more pizza diet!

578
00:35:33,056 --> 00:35:37,056
Whoa, he's stealing the cookies! Kill him!

579
00:35:37,056 --> 00:35:41,056
My gun... it doesn't work!

580
00:35:41,056 --> 00:35:45,056
He's texting while driving! We have to put him down!

581
00:35:45,056 --> 00:35:46,556
That was so good!

582
00:35:47,056 --> 00:35:51,056
Okay, I think you are done. / You've run out of bullets.

583
00:35:51,056 --> 00:35:54,056
Gigi, point it away from yourself. / Oh, no, no, no!

584
00:35:57,056 --> 00:36:00,056
Okay!

585
00:36:00,056 --> 00:36:05,056
Wait, it's time to reveal Gigi's score!

586
00:36:05,056 --> 00:36:07,056
They're real, they're real!

587
00:36:07,056 --> 00:36:10,056
Okay, the final score for Gigi... / Do it!

588
00:36:10,056 --> 00:36:15,056
You...

589
00:36:15,056 --> 00:36:17,056
I'm so tired! / Eight! You got eight!

590
00:36:17,056 --> 00:36:21,056
Yeah! Eight!

591
00:36:24,056 --> 00:36:27,056
It's your turn, Raora Panthera! / It's me!

592
00:36:28,056 --> 00:36:31,056
Yeah, big cat means... / Big gun? Me?

593
00:36:32,056 --> 00:36:35,056
Yeah, let's go. Let's face the gun!

594
00:36:36,056 --> 00:36:38,056
It's not real, you're not gonna die. / I practice...

595
00:36:39,056 --> 00:36:42,056
Wait, what? What do I do again?

596
00:36:42,056 --> 00:36:45,056
You shoot those targets, and you shoot the ones that are bad.

597
00:36:46,056 --> 00:36:50,056
Bad ones? / How do I know which one is bad?

598
00:36:51,056 --> 00:36:54,056
That's up to you to decide as a member of Justice.

599
00:36:55,056 --> 00:36:59,056
Ready? / I'm ready! / Ready, set, go!

600
00:36:59,056 --> 00:37:01,056
Go, go, go, get him!

601
00:37:02,056 --> 00:37:05,056
Okay, okay... shoot, shoot, shoot!

602
00:37:05,056 --> 00:37:10,056
Behind, Raora, behind! A little to the left!

603
00:37:10,056 --> 00:37:13,056
You were supposed to shoot this one! / Oh, really?

604
00:37:14,056 --> 00:37:19,056
Oh, look, he's texting while driving! / Where?

605
00:37:19,056 --> 00:37:22,056
Get him! / I can't... I can't hit it.

606
00:37:22,056 --> 00:37:25,056
He's texting! Oh God, that guy is a menace!

607
00:37:25,056 --> 00:37:30,056
Liz? Liz? / No, don't kill Liz! / I shot Liz...

608
00:37:30,056 --> 00:37:33,056
I'm right here, that's an impostor! / You killed Liz!

609
00:37:34,056 --> 00:37:38,056
Don't kill him! / Kill him! Kill him!

610
00:37:38,056 --> 00:37:43,056
Did you get him? / No! That's a 'No Shoot'!

611
00:37:44,056 --> 00:37:48,056
Raora with the god eyes, huh? He's stealing cookies!

612
00:37:49,056 --> 00:37:54,056
Get him! Kill him! He's stealing the cookies!

613
00:37:55,056 --> 00:37:58,056
Hey, but he's gone! / Why didn't you kill him?!

614
00:38:00,056 --> 00:38:03,056
Oh right, next... Come on, get the next one!

615
00:38:04,056 --> 00:38:07,056
Oh, cute! / No, he's stealing fairy mushrooms!

616
00:38:08,056 --> 00:38:12,056
Get him, get him, get him! / Hey, I shot...

617
00:38:13,056 --> 00:38:15,056
Ah, that's a 'No Shoot'.

618
00:38:16,056 --> 00:38:20,056
Kill it! Kill it! Kill it!

619
00:38:21,056 --> 00:38:23,056
Yeah! Kill it!

620
00:38:24,056 --> 00:38:29,056
Oh, that's bad! / Raora, get the piggy bank!

621
00:38:29,056 --> 00:38:34,056
Get the piggy bank! Yeah, shoot it!

622
00:38:35,056 --> 00:38:39,056
Ah! He's on the loose! / It jumps real fast.

623
00:38:40,056 --> 00:38:45,056
Wait, no, don't shoot it! / No?

624
00:38:46,056 --> 00:38:50,056
Yay, cucumber for dinner! / Yeah!

625
00:38:51,056 --> 00:38:55,056
Oh, money! / Do we want money?

626
00:38:56,056 --> 00:38:59,056
This is the Gigi texting. / What's wrong with that?

627
00:39:00,056 --> 00:39:03,056
Yeah!

628
00:39:04,056 --> 00:39:09,056
That was great, Raora! That was really good!

629
00:39:10,056 --> 00:39:13,056
Really good for a kitty. / Can I shoot something else?

630
00:39:14,056 --> 00:39:19,056
Can I go after criminals? / Gigi, save the score.

631
00:39:20,056 --> 00:39:24,056
Do you want to know how much? / I want to know!

632
00:39:24,056 --> 00:39:28,056
I want to know! / Hold my hand, I need to tell you.

633
00:39:29,056 --> 00:39:33,056
Your score was... four! / Four?

634
00:39:34,056 --> 00:39:39,056
You did it on purpose, because there's four of us!

635
00:39:40,056 --> 00:39:44,056
Justice! / Justice!

636
00:39:45,056 --> 00:39:49,056
And the training is complete! Huzzah!

637
00:39:50,056 --> 00:39:59,056
And the winner is... all of us! Yeah!

638
00:40:01,064 --> 00:40:04,064
At the loser! Loser! The loser! Loser!

639
00:40:05,264 --> 00:40:08,564
Oh, it's okay, Gigi, you're the freaking loser.

640
00:40:11,064 --> 00:40:15,564
Hey, I just wanted to make you win because I'm the strongest with my god eyes, so...

641
00:40:15,864 --> 00:40:18,064
Also, Elizabeth, what's that behind your back?

642
00:40:18,264 --> 00:40:20,064
What's behind my back?

643
00:40:20,164 --> 00:40:21,864
What's behind your back?

644
00:40:21,864 --> 00:40:23,064
What's behind my back?

645
00:40:23,164 --> 00:40:25,564
What's behind your back?

646
00:40:28,064 --> 00:40:30,064
You can't do that!

647
00:40:30,064 --> 00:40:33,064
You can't do that! She's mad!

648
00:40:33,264 --> 00:40:35,564
She's mad!

649
00:40:36,564 --> 00:40:39,564
She's mad!

650
00:40:40,064 --> 00:40:42,564
Cecilia! Cecilia!

651
00:40:42,664 --> 00:40:44,564
Cecilia!

652
00:40:45,064 --> 00:40:50,064
Traffic Enforcement Training
[Title: Traffic Enforcement Training]

653
00:40:46,564 --> 00:40:50,064
The next training is Traffic Enforcement Training.

654
00:40:50,064 --> 00:40:54,564
This duty requires accurately assessing the violation

655
00:40:54,564 --> 00:40:57,564
and processing it correctly.

656
00:40:57,564 --> 00:41:02,564
However, in the field, unexpected behavior

657
00:41:02,564 --> 00:41:04,864
can sometimes shake an officer's judgment.

658
00:41:04,864 --> 00:41:08,564
Can Justice stay unfazed in any situation

659
00:41:08,564 --> 00:41:11,064
and carry out the appropriate response?

660
00:41:14,064 --> 00:41:16,864
We did it, boys. Good job, my goons.

661
00:41:16,864 --> 00:41:19,064
Oh no, a cop car. Run!

662
00:41:20,064 --> 00:41:23,064
Oh no!

663
00:41:27,064 --> 00:41:29,264
My goon, goon, do the voice, do the voice.

664
00:41:29,264 --> 00:41:31,064
Okay, boss.

665
00:41:31,064 --> 00:41:33,264
Buonasera.
Good evening.

666
00:41:33,264 --> 00:41:35,064
Good afternoon.

667
00:41:35,064 --> 00:41:36,564
What's all this then?

668
00:41:36,564 --> 00:41:39,564
You know what? I pulled you over... That was really cool.

669
00:41:39,564 --> 00:41:42,564
Oh my god, you did it again. Oh cool.

670
00:41:42,564 --> 00:41:43,864
Silenzio!
Silence!

671
00:41:43,864 --> 00:41:47,064
Don't act like you don't know anything!

672
00:41:47,064 --> 00:41:50,064
You blew right through the stop sign!

673
00:41:50,564 --> 00:41:54,064
We are just really in a hurry right now.

674
00:41:54,064 --> 00:41:57,864
My husband, he's pregnant.

675
00:41:58,264 --> 00:42:01,264
Can I see your driver's license, please?

676
00:42:01,264 --> 00:42:04,564
Oh yes, yes. Do you have your driver's license?

677
00:42:05,064 --> 00:42:08,564
Driver's license? We don't have time.

678
00:42:09,064 --> 00:42:12,264
He's really pregnant. I am so pregnant.

679
00:42:12,864 --> 00:42:14,564
His water just broke!

680
00:42:14,564 --> 00:42:17,564
Oh, we have to go to the hospital!

681
00:42:17,564 --> 00:42:20,064
We have to go to the hospital right now, please!

